<br />\n要改搭船過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  再call 車"},{"pid":"4fabcfd73b590b6c21720c8325fc1cce0b00c890","tid":863880,"uid":55192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到我好感動 原來香港仲有巴打呢種員工 香港有希望喇！<br />\n獅子山精神就靠巴打你呢一種人延續落去啦！"},{"pid":"426b7171d9d03933c469f2ebcc5dd1dff3fd971a","tid":863880,"uid":141869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"你老闆試緊你份人誠唔誠實，<br />\n你冇搭巴士最好唔好去claim,<br />\n否則出年想加人工都幾難"},{"pid":"15298c23d521f908b270108985552906fbe464a6","tid":863880,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"連登啲細蚊仔真係無主見一尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個月前個post成堆負皮<br />\n依家見人正皮又跟正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dcbc39912d255bf4c812292418150647fc309e","tid":863880,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"426b7171d9d03933c469f2ebcc5dd1dff3fd971a","tid":863880,"uid":141869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"你老闆試緊你份人誠唔誠實，<br />\n你冇搭巴士最好唔好去claim,<br />\n否則出年想加人工都幾難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"sorry老闆"},{"pid":"c7f5e4baa4efefd6d802f54ae00670e05da6cbea","tid":863880,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"仆街又要ot,本身收5點，呢家仲係大埔"}]}